WHAT THE FISH 🐟 Salmon sperm is currently making waves in the realm of skincare. Bazaar India dives into what makes this celebrity-approved procedure stand out and if it’s truly worth the buzz | Harper’s Bazaar India | December 2024

Sushi, salads, bisques—salmon is the delectable main character in many a meal. Add sperm and facial to the equation, and you have yourself a whole different picture. To a lot of ‘sane’ people, a salmon sperm facial sounds outlandish. But, those ‘insane’ few who have kept up with theKardashians long enough would tell you that when it comes to innovation, beauty treatments leave no stone unturned. And the salmon sperm facial is no different. Experts @drswethadilip from @thewhitedoorindia, @dr.chytra from @kosmoderma, and @drkiransays from @isyaderm weigh in on K beauty’s latest trend!

Words: @tatianadias23 for @bazaarindia

In All Fairness | Harper’s Bazaar India | June July 2025 issue 

Whitening, lightening, brightening the skincare lexicon has evolved with time, but is the intention still the same?

For decades, the Indian obsession​ with fair skin has been unabashed.​ In the realm of beauty, years of​ conditioning have especially led​ generations to associate fairness with success,​ confidence, and let’s not forget, being lovely.​ Over the last few years, however, this​ archaic narrative has seen a major shift.​ Skincare terminology no longer promotes​ whitening or lightening, but rather, has​ evolved to brightening solutions, creating a​ paper-thin line between the two terms​. Experts @anjalimahto @dr.chytra @drkiransays dive deep into this controversial skincare topic.

Words: @tatianadias23 for @bazaarindia

latestPosts.caption:
Not just sun care, it’s skincare too ☀️ I got to host a byte-size, informative event with @skinspired.in x Heliocare, a Spanish sun protection brand synonymous with derm-approved sunscreens. What’s not common knowledge, however, is that they offer more than SPF numbers. 

Formulated with a unique Fernblock Technology, these sunscreens are designed to work on your skin at a cellular level even after the sun goes down! It tackles pigmentation, fine lines, wrinkles, fights free radical damage, and much more. 

They offer a range of sunscreens for different skin types and concerns, allowing you to choose the perfect fit for you. Now there’s literally no excuse to skip your sunscreen 🌞

latestPosts.caption:
For those who can never find their perfect foundation match, @luarbeauty.in’s Shade Shifter Drops are a game-changer. Available in two shades — SHIFT UP and SHIFT DOWN — these mini drops allow you to customise any foundation to perfectly match your skin tone. Whether you’re dealing with a bad post-holiday tan or can’t get your neck to match your face skin tone, you no longer have to reach out to a whole new foundation for it! These drops are an affordable and more sustainable alternative ✨

What’s to love:
💧A little goes a long way –– a drop of the Shade Shifter is enough to tweak your foundation shade. Feel free to play around with the amount to customise the shade according to your skin tone
💧It blends well with most foundation formulas, has a lightweight finish, and offers medium coverage
💧Each bottle is priced at INR 500 — which makes it pocket-friendly, as opposed to purchasing a new foundation
